VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (?i)\.debug\s*=\s*True|\$debug\s*=\s*true|DEBUG\s*=\s*True|IsDebuggingEnabled\s*=\s*true
WHEN EXPR MISSING:(?i)\b(release|production)\b
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects the presence of sensitive debug information in application settings.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Sensitive Debug Information.
